                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S.C.chapter 15</xref>,
Cost Accounting Standards (48 CFR Chapter 99) (see <xref href="FAR-i1113603.dita#i1113603"
                              base="i1113603"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">12.214</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
